author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
Welcome back to TACTICAL AWARENESS - a Canadian Podcast about Corvus Belli’s landmark Sci-Fi Wargame; Infinity N5. Come along with our hosts Ash, Owen and Dan for a whole new ITS Edition of Infinity! 

Want to mix and match medium-awesome Heavy Infantry to your heart's content? The State Empire has the faction for you! The Invincible Army allows for a ton of customization in forces with a huge array of 2 Vita options in this Heroes to Zeros!
